			<h3><span><a class="sharelink" rel="nofollow" href="#p456" onclick="return false;">Поделиться</a><strong>2</strong><a class="permalink" rel="nofollow" href="http://lestnitsa.bbmy.ru/viewtopic.php?id=122#p456">Сб, 19 Мар 2011 16:23</a></span></h3>
			<div class="container">
				<IDXSKIP><div class="post-author">
